# Intentionally committed (NOT ignored): GitHub Pages serves files straight from
# this branch, so the CDMX map's built assets (projects/cdmx-map/assets/) and its
# GeoJSON data (projects/cdmx-map/data/) must stay tracked. The source for that
# app lives in github.com/ignacio-ireta/cdmx-convenience-map.
#
# Likewise, the ETF report artifacts (projects/etf-portfolio-research/reports/)
# are committed so the showcase page can embed them same-origin. They are synced
